// Manual Eq ignores `version` (id-only equality), but derived Hash includes it.
// Two items with same id but different versions are Eq (eq says so) but hash
// to different values — `a == b` does NOT imply `hash(a) == hash(b)`. HashMap
// will silently lose entries when a lookup uses a different version than insert.
#[derive(Hash)] // includes version
